<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Welcome | Vasti Vikas Prakalp</title>

    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/aos@2.3.4/dist/aos.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />

    <style>
      * {
        box-sizing: border-box;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }

      body {
        font-family: "Segoe UI", Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        background: url("/images/bg.jpg") no-repeat center center fixed;
        background-size: cover;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        min-height: 100vh;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        color: #333;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .overlay {
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        height: 100%;
        width: 100%;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
        z-index: 0;
      }

      .main-background {
        background: url("/images/background1.jpg") no-repeat center top;
        background-size: cover;
        background-attachment: fixed;
        width: 100%;
        padding-top: 40px;
        padding-bottom: 60px;
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
      }

      .main-content {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 400px;
        margin: auto;
        z-index: 2;
        position: relative;
      }

      .logo {
        width: 150px;
        margin: 0 auto 20px;
      }

      .container {
        background: white;
        padding: 30px 20px;
        border-radius: 15px;
        box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
      }

      h2 {
        color: #5a50ea;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        font-size: 24px;
      }

      .btn {
        display: block;
        width: 100%;
        padding: 15px;
        margin: 10px 0;
        background: #246bfd;
        color: white;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-size: 18px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        border: none;
        cursor: pointer;
        transition: background 0.3s ease;
      }

      .btn:hover {
        background: #1a5cdc;
      }

      .about {
        max-width: 700px;
        margin: 40px auto 20px;
        padding: 0 20px;
        font-size: 17px;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
        border-radius: 12px;
        box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
        z-index: 2;
        position: relative;
      }

      .gallery-section {
        max-width: 700px;
        width: 90%;
        margin: 60px auto 20px;
        z-index: 1;
        position: relative;
      }

      .gallery-image {
        width: 100%;
        height: auto;
        border-radius: 15px;
        box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
        margin-bottom: 40px;
      }

      @media (max-width: 500px) {
        .container {
          padding: 20px 15px;
        }
        .btn {
          font-size: 16px;
          padding: 12px;
        }
        .about {
          font-size: 15px;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="overlay"></div>

    <div class="main-background">
      <div class="main-content">
        <img src="/images/logo2.jpg" alt="Signal Shala Logo" class="logo" />

        <!-- Login Card -->
        <div class="container">
          <h2>Login As</h2>
          <a href="/auth/login/teacher" class="btn">Teacher</a>
          <a href="/auth/login/coordinator" class="btn">Coordinator</a>
          <a href="/auth/login/head" class="btn">Head</a>
        </div>

        <div class="about">
          <h2 style="color: #ec4141; margin-bottom: 10px">
            Vasti Vikas Prakalp
          </h2>
          <h3 style="color: #0c0c0c; margin-bottom: 10px">
            Run by Samarth Bharat Vyaspeeth
          </h3>
          <p>
            They are the children of jobless parents under tremendous social
            pressure. Their lives lack structure and are torn apart by
            superstitions. These children have parents crushed by money lenders
            and debt, and the social system does not recognize their existence.
            Their health needs are neglected, and they face a bleak future,
            living only for today. Their family lives are disturbed, and they
            are shunned by the so-called elite of society. These children endure
            harsh and adverse conditions. The Vasti Vikas Prakalp strives to
            bring such children into the mainstream of society by addressing not
            only their educational needs but also their health and emotional
            well-being.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="gallery-section">
      <img src="/images/img1.jpg" class="gallery-image" data-aos="fade-up" />
      <img
        src="/images/img2.jpg"
        class="gallery-image"
        data-aos="fade-up"
        data-aos-delay="100"
      />
      <img
        src="/images/img3.jpg"
        class="gallery-image"
        data-aos="fade-up"
        data-aos-delay="200"
      />
      <img
        src="/images/img4.jpg"
        class="gallery-image"
        data-aos="fade-up"
        data-aos-delay="300"
      />
      <img
        src="/images/img5.jpg"
        class="gallery-image"
        data-aos="fade-up"
        data-aos-delay="400"
      />
      <img
        src="/images/img6.jpg"
        class="gallery-image"
        data-aos="fade-up"
        data-aos-delay="500"
      />
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/aos@2.3.4/dist/aos.js"></script>
    <script>
      AOS.init({
        duration: 1000,
        once: true,
      });
    </script>
  </body>
</html>
